steps because it's

00:19:42.020 --> 00:19:45.140
easy to apply
boundary conditions.

00:19:45.140 --> 00:19:48.820
And so these are all just
computationally tricky things

00:19:48.820 --> 00:19:50.470
that are wonderful.

00:19:50.470 --> 00:19:54.700
And we don't worry
about, is there

00:19:54.700 --> 00:19:57.760
