like a delta function

00:19:57.760 --> 00:19:58.910
or a vertical step?

00:19:58.910 --> 00:19:59.410
No.

00:19:59.410 --> 00:20:00.700
There isn't.

00:20:00.700 --> 00:20:03.400
But everything you get
easily, mathematically,

00:20:03.400 --> 00:20:06.040
from these simple
things is great.

