00:27:19.060 --> 00:27:24.180
So if this is not Hermitian,
and this is not Hermitian,

00:27:24.180 --> 00:27:27.560
but that we're defining
something that is Hermitian,

00:27:27.560 --> 00:27:30.790
so let's just put a
